      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so busy and i hate having to make an appointment just for something like this. i feel like i know my body better than anyone else lol. honestly the nausea is so bad im missing work. if i just slowly decrease the sertraline over a few days while starting the st johns wort, would that basically just bridge the gap? i just want a natural way to handle this without all the chemical side effects.",
